{"word":"H3256 - יָסַר - yâçar - yaw-sar' - Bind","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָסַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>yâçar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>yaw-sar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Bind"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தண்டி, கண்டி, எச்சரிக்கையைாயிரு, புத்திகேள், தண்டிக்கப்படு, அடங்கு, குணப்படு, புத்தியடை, போதி, உணர்த்து, புத்திசொல், உபதேசி, சிட்சைசெய், சிட்சி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to chasten, to discipline, to instruct, to admonish"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to chasten, to admonish"},{"paragraph":"2) to instruct"},{"paragraph":"3) to discipline"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to let oneself be chastened or corrected or admonished"},{"paragraph":"c) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to discipline, to correct"},{"paragraph":"2) to chasten, to chastize"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>chastise</i>, literally (with blows) or figuratively (with words); hence to <i>instruct: - </i>bind, chasten, chastise, correct, instruct, punish, reform, reprove, sore, teach."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3250 - יִסֹּור - yiççôwr - yis-sore'/3250\">H3250</a>, <a href=\"#/H3256 - יָסַר - yâçar - yaw-sar'/3256\">H3256</a>, <a href=\"#/H4148 - מוּסָר - mûwçâr - moo-sawr'/4148\">H4148</a>, <a href=\"#/H4561 - מֹסָר - môçâr - mo-sawr'/4561\">H4561</a>"}]}